name: Kale Ceasar
description: Behold the emperor of salads! Roasted chicken strutting its stuff with tomatoes, parmesan crisps standing in as the royal guard, shaved parmesan for that aristocratic flair, and a legion of shredded kale and chopped romaine. Finished with a lime squeeze and caesar dressing that's so good, it could start its own empire

name: Shroomami
description: A dish so rich in flavor, it's priced like a treasure! Roasted tofu and a warm portobello mix that's practically a mushroom party, cucumbers and basil doing the salsa, with a sprinkle of shredded cabbage. Roasted almonds and wild rice join the fun, all dressed in miso sesame ginger that's the life of the party

name: Miso Glazed Salmon
description: Dive into an ocean of flavor with miso glazed salmon that's been swimming in deliciousness. Accompanied by avocado bodyguards, cucumber fans, pickled onion paparazzi, and crispy onion confetti. Served on a bed of white rice times two, with nori sesame seasoning and spicy cashew dressing that's the real catch of the day

name: Za'atar Crunch
description: A culinary symphony with blackened chicken on lead vocals, olives and shredded cabbage on backup, za’atar breadcrumbs on guitar, chickpeas on drums, and goat cheese on the keyboard. Wild rice and shredded kale join the band, with balsamic vinaigrette as the manager making sure every bite is a hit

name: Super Green Goddess
description: Unleash your inner deity with this divine mix. Chickpeas and roasted sweet potatoes walk on clouds, raw carrots and spicy broccoli bring the thunder, shredded cabbage and roasted almonds sprinkle in some magic. Baby spinach and shredded kale lay the green carpet, with green goddess ranch dressing reigning supreme

name: Elote Bowl
description: Roasted corn + fajita veg, shredded cabbage, tomatoes, cilantro, goat cheese, tortilla chips, organic warm quinoa, arugula, lime cilantro jalapeño vinaigrette.

name: Italian Chopped
description: Salami, spicy banana peppers, tomatoes, cucumbers, chickpeas, red onions, shaved parmesan, chopped romaine, shredded kale, red wine vinaigrette.

name: Buffalo Chicken
description: Blackened chicken, pickled onions, tomatoes, raw carrots, cilantro, blue cheese, za’atar breadcrumbs, shredded kale, chopped romaine, sweetgreen hot sauce, caesar

name: Garden Cobb
description: Avocado, hard boiled egg, roasted sweet potatoes, tomatoes, red onions, blue cheese, roasted almonds, spring mix, chopped romaine, balsamic vinaigrette.

name: Fish Taco
description: Miso glazed salmon, avocado, shredded cabbage, cilantro, tortilla chips, herbed quinoa, arugula, sweetgreen hot sauce, lime cilantro jalapeño vinaigrette

name: Little Harvest
description: Roasted chicken, warm roasted sweet potatoes, apples, sunflower seeds, balsamic vinaigrette *Select sg restaurants only.

name: Honest Kids Apple Juice
description: Organic juice with no added sugar or artificial sweeteners.

name: Siete Sea Salt Potato Chips
description: Crafted with the best kind of basics: potatoes, avocado oil and sea salt.

name: Hummus + Focaccia
description: Locally baked rosemary focaccia breadsticks paired with smooth hummus.

name: Crispy Rice Treat
description: Crispy organic brown rice, quinoa, and puffed millet—naturally sweetened with honey date caramel and just 6g of sugar. *This treat is gluten-free but contains common allergens, including dairy + tree nuts (coconuts).

name: Hu Cashews + Vanilla Bean Hunks
description: Organic snackable dark chocolate covered cashews with a pinch of sea salt and no refined sugar. *This product is gluten-free and vegan but contains cashew & coconut. May contain dairy, peanuts & other tree nuts.

name: Jasmine Green Tea
description: Antioxidant rich, with organic soba and wild grown yaupon.

name: Hibiscus Berry Clover Tea
description: Refreshing crimson clover tea brightened with tangy hibiscus

name: Open Water Still Water
description: In An Eco-friendly Aluminum Bottle For Plastic Free Oceans

name: Health-Ade Kombucha Pink Lady Apple
description: Effervescent probiotic tea brewed with a hint of apple cider (12g sugar)

name: Ghia Spritz-Ginger
description: Non-alcoholic apéritif packed with pure, natural botanicals and ginger
